name: ExperienceTyrol
0:
”Alexa, ask Experience Tyrol for an activity.”
”Tell me something about Tyrol.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: experience tyrol
des: Experience Tyrol knows the best insider tips, helps you plan your next hike, shows you the most beautiful inns and doesn't let you down even when it rains. It is your digital information office for at home or on the go and ensures that you don't miss any Tyrolean highlights on vacation. On top of that, you will learn Tyrolean and will soon shine with the knowledge of the locals! Some skill content can be in German.
